>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
replace

<item name="MariaDB-(10.2-10.6)" xsi:type="string">^10\.[2-6]\.</item>

To

<item name="MariaDB-(10.2-10.11)" xsi:type="string">^10\.([2-9]|10|11)\.</item>

